§7§oXnet is a medium-power logistics tool.

It is the recommended way to manage passive automations of lots of different items coming in and out of machines.

It is much more performant than enderIO conduits for item transfer.

Xnet can also be used to mode energy, although the transfer rate may not be high enough for all applications.

Because of a bug with the mod, conduits are still better than Xnet for fluid automation.
